    "summary": {
      "videoPrompt": "A young woman in a modest living room, smirking calmly while sipping tea. An older woman with permed hair and gold jewelry stands red-faced, angrily pointing and spitting. The older woman suddenly farts loudly, looking mortified. Tension, awkward silence, dramatic lighting.",
